 " = 1.5PN Spin-Orbit coupling"
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9858695228215437`*^9, {3.985869586141964*^9, 
   3.985869588761249*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"336232dd-4881-4824-bfdd-\
c0a168d2f892"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["h", "ss"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
