Cell["\<\
Run the entire notebook (Evaluation --> Evaluate Notebook). That\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s it! \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.985869522833911*^9, {3.985875484297421*^9, 3.98587549087123*^9}, {
